title: The End (CRE116)
description:
A Classic RISK! episode from our first two years! In our sixteenth episode, storytellers Eliza Skinner, Martin Dockery, Cyndi Freeman, and Ryan Paulson share stories of endings, some happy, some not. Recorded live at the 92Y Tribeca.

author: Kevin@RISK-show.com (Eliza Skinner, Martin Dockery, Trevor Jude Smith, Ryan Paulson, kevin Allison, Dan Rosen, David Buchs, Tom Waits, Cyndi Freeman, Adam Griffin)
